  "title": "BRAND AMBASSADOR/SALES ASSOCIATE",
  "description": "<h2>Not Sure What’s Next? Start Here.</h2><p><strong>Training Provided | Real Growth | No Experience Needed</strong></p><p>If you’re early in your career and feeling unsure about your next move, this role gives you <strong>direction, skills, and momentum</strong>—not just a job.</p><p>You’ll gain real-world experience, confidence, and communication skills while working with established brands.</p><h3>What You’ll Do</h3><ul><li><p>Represent brands at <strong>live events and roadshows</strong></p></li><li><p>Engage the public and build strong communication skills</p></li><li><p>Learn professional presentation and persuasion techniques</p></li><li><p>Grow confidence through hands-on, people-facing experience</p></li></ul><h3>What You’ll Get</h3><ul><li><p><strong>Structured training from Day One</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>1-to-1 mentorship</strong> and daily guidance</p></li><li><p>Networking and <strong>travel opportunities</strong></p></li><li><p>A clear, performance-based path to <strong>leadership roles</strong></p></li></ul><h3>This Role Is For You If You</h3><ul><li><p>Want to grow but aren’t sure where to start</p></li><li><p>Are coachable and open to feedback</p></li><li><p>Enjoy interacting with people</p></li><li><p>Value personal development and progress</p></li></ul><p><strong>No experience required.</strong><br />We hire for <strong>potential</strong>, not resumes.</p><p><strong>Apply now</strong> and build a strong foundation for your career.</p>",
